com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.transaction

Class SCUITransactionContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.platform.transaction.SCUITransactionContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISCUITransactionContext

    public class SCUITransactionContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISCUITransactionContext
    This class is implementaion of ISCUITransactionContext for Platform Impl. It is just a wrapper class on Environment used as transaction context in plaform afc. All methods, begin, commit, rollback, end are empty. Environment, which is used in platform afc, can be added as a transaction object in this class. asmishra
